<tr><td colspan=2><font color=#FFFFFF size="5" face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif">Hijacked Planes Destroy Twin Towers, Burn Pentagon</font></td></tr>
<tr><td><font color=#FFFFFF face="arial" size="2">DeckTech reports on Wed Sep 12 2001 </font></td><td align=right><font face="arial" size="2" color=#FFFFFF>DeckTech Update</font></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2><font color=#FFFFFF face="arial" size="2"><img src="/news/images/towers.jpg" align="right">Three planes commandeered by unknown hijackers slammed into the Pentagon and New York's landmark World Trade Center on Tuesday, demolishing the twin 110-story towers that were once the tallest buildings in the world and possibly burying thousands of people alive.<br />
<br />
My thoughts and prayers are with those people that suffered from these atrocities. In times like these many things seem trivial and unimportant. <br />
<br />
I hope you will play it safe and keep your traveling, and exposure to monuments, government buildings, large meeting centers, and other high-risk areas to a minimum.  Stay alive, and donate blood if you can. <br />
<br />
If you know something about the incidents you can call 1-866-483-5137 or submit information to <A href="http://www.ifccfbi.gov/">http://www.ifccfbi.gov/</A>. <br />
<br />
by David Akers  <p><small>edited by DeckTech on Wed Sep 12 2001 </small></font></td></tr>
